Get 5 stars simply for being in Vegas and its free.  I can assure you most everything else touristy comes at a cost in Vegas.

Show is multiple times a day, but is a little more frequent in the evenings. 

The crowds start to form before the show even begins, so if you arrive just as it begins you will have to stand behind people already posted up along the banisters that surround the fountains.

The music and water is a relaxing break and ends almost as quickly as it begins.